data.description: Located on a prime corner lot, 2524 SW 12th Street is a charming ranch-style home offering comfort and convenience. The main floor features a spacious living room and an open kitchen with a breakfast bar/island, perfect for entertaining. With two bedrooms on the main level and a fully finished walkout basement, the home provides flexible living spaces, including a large family room, an additional bedroom, and a 3/4 bath. Outdoor amenities include a fenced backyard with a deck and covered patio, ideal for outdoor activities and relaxation. Completing this property is a 2-stall attached garage, adding convenience and storage space. Well-maintained and move-in ready, this home presents an excellent opportunity to enjoy versatile living in a desirable location. Schedule your private showing today!
